    <h1>Ideal Customer Profile (ICP)</h1>
    <p class="description">A data-driven description of the company or customer type that gets the most value from your product and can be served most profitably. The filter that tells marketing which leads to pursue and which to pass on.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
