              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>List your 10 best customers and identify shared characteristics: industry, company size, revenue range, tech stack, how they found you, and what problem they were solving. Interview 3-5 of them to validate the patterns. Test the resulting ICP against new prospects for 90 days, then refine based on which new customers convert, retain, and expand.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
